title: Blanche (given name)
text: Blanche is a feminine <a href="given%20name">given name</a>. It means "<a href="white">white</a>" in <a href="French%20language">French</a>, derived from the <a href="Late%20Latin">Late Latin</a> word "blancus". It is a popular 20th-century name in <a href="England">England</a>.
